==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin prefix ''[[im-]]'', "im-", + ''[[bibere]]'', "to drink".

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪb|-aɪb]]

===Verb===
'''imbibe''', present participle '''[[imbibing]]''', past and past participle '''[[imbibed]]'''

# to [[drink]] (used frequently of alcoholic [[beverage]]s)
# to [[take]] in; as, to imbibe knowledge

====Translations====

*Czech : [[nasávat]], [[nasát]], [[vstřebat]]

